lass=\"name\">Simp</span>.<span class=\"name\">SimprocOLeanEntry</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/df668f00e6c08cb63661aacc43d0e83388e2c60d/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.lean#L224-L225","name":"Lean.Meta.Simp.instAndThenDSimproc","line":224,"kind":"instance","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.instAndThenDSimproc","doc":""},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">instance</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.instAndThenDSimproc\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Simp</span>.<span class=\"name\">instAndThenDSimproc</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#AndThen\">AndThen</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.DSimproc\">Lean.Meta.Simp.DSimproc</a></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/df668f00e6c08cb63661aacc43d0e83388e2c60d/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.lean#L217-L222","name":"Lean.Meta.Simp.dandThen","line":217,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.dandThen","doc":""},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.dandThen\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Simp</span>.<span class=\"name\">dandThen</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(f : <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.DSimproc\">Lean.Meta.Simp.DSimproc</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(g : <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.DSimproc\">Lean.Meta.Simp.DSimproc</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.DSimproc\">Lean.Meta.Simp.DSimproc</a></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/df668f00e6c08cb63661aacc43d0e83388e2c60d/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.lean#L213-L214","name":"Lean.Meta.Simp.instAndThenSimproc","line":213,"kind":"instance","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.instAndThenSimproc","doc":""},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">instance</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.instAndThenSimproc\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Simp</span>.<span class=\"name\">instAndThenSimproc</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#AndThen\">AndThen</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Simproc\">Lean.Meta.Simp.Simproc</a></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/df668f00e6c08cb63661aacc43d0e83388e2c60d/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.lean#L206-L211","name":"Lean.Meta.Simp.andThen","line":206,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.andThen","doc":"\"Compose\" the two given simplification procedures. We use the following semantics.\n- If `f` produces `done` or `visit`, then return `f`'s result.\n- If `f` produces `continue`, then apply `g` to new expression returned by `f`.\n\nSee `Simp.Step` type.\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.andThen\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Simp</span>.<span class=\"name\">andThen</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(f : <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Simproc\">Lean.Meta.Simp.Simproc</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(g : <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Simproc\">Lean.Meta.Simp.Simproc</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Simproc\">Lean.Meta.Simp.Simproc</a></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/df668f00e6c08cb63661aacc43d0e83388e2c60d/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.lean#L191-L196","name":"Lean.Meta.Simp.mkEqTransResultStep","line":191,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.mkEqTransResultStep","doc":""},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.mkEqTransResultStep\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Simp</span>.<span class=\"name\">mkEqTransResultStep</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(r : <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Result\">Lean.Meta.Simp.Result</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(s : <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Step\">Lean.Meta.Simp.Step</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Basic.html#Lean.Meta.MetaM\">Lean.MetaM</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Step\">Lean.Meta.Simp.Step</a></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/df668f00e6c08cb63661aacc43d0e83388e2c60d/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.lean#L184-L189","name":"Lean.TransformStep.toStep","line":184,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.TransformStep.toStep","doc":""},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.TransformStep.toStep\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">TransformStep</span>.<span class=\"name\">toStep</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(s : <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Transform.html#Lean.TransformStep\">Lean.TransformStep</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Step\">Lean.Meta.Simp.Step</a></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/df668f00e6c08cb63661aacc43d0e83388e2c60d/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.lean#L182-L182","name":"Lean.Meta.Simp.DSimproc","line":182,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.DSimproc","doc":"Similar to `Simproc`, but resulting expression should be definitionally equal to the input one.\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.DSimproc\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Simp</span>.<span class=\"name\">DSimproc</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/df668f00e6c08cb63661aacc43d0e83388e2c60d/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.lean#L177-L177","name":"Lean.Meta.Simp.DStep","line":177,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.DStep","doc":""},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.DStep\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Simp</span>.<span class=\"name\">DStep</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/df668f00e6c08cb63661aacc43d0e83388e2c60d/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.lean#L175-L175","name":"Lean.Meta.Simp.Simproc","line":175,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Simproc","doc":"A simplification procedure. Recall that we have `pre` and `post` procedures.\nSee `Step`.\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Simproc\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Simp</span>.<span class=\"name\">Simproc</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/df668f00e6c08cb63661aacc43d0e83388e2c60d/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.lean#L169-L169","name":"Lean.Meta.Simp.instInhabitedStep","line":169,"kind":"instance","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.instInhabitedStep","doc":""},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">instance</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.instInhabitedStep\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Simp</span>.<span class=\"name\">instInhabitedStep</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Inhabited\">Inhabited</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Step\">Lean.Meta.Simp.Step</a></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/df668f00e6c08cb63661aacc43d0e83388e2c60d/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.lean#L162-L168","name":"Lean.Meta.Simp.Step.continue","line":162,"kind":"ctor","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Step.continue","doc":"For `pre` procedures, continue transformation by visiting subexpressions, and then\nexecuting `post` procedures.\n\nFor `post` procedures, this is equivalent to returning `visit`.\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">constructor</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Step.continue\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Simp</span>.<span class=\"name\">Step</span>.<span class=\"name\">continue</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(e? : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#optParam\">optParam</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Result\">Lean.Meta.Simp.Result</a></span>)</span> <span class=\"fn\">none</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Step\">Lean.Meta.Simp.Step</a></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/df668f00e6c08cb63661aacc43d0e83388e2c60d/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.lean#L155-L161","name":"Lean.Meta.Simp.Step.visit","line":155,"kind":"ctor","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Step.visit","doc":"For `pre` procedures, the resulting expression is passed to `pre` again.\n\nFor `post` procedures, the resulting expression is passed to `pre` again IF\n`Simp.Config.singlePass := false` and resulting expression is not equal to initial expression.\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">constructor</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Step.visit\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Simp</span>.<span class=\"name\">Step</span>.<span class=\"name\">visit</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(e : <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Result\">Lean.Meta.Simp.Result</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Step\">Lean.Meta.Simp.Step</a></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/df668f00e6c08cb63661aacc43d0e83388e2c60d/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.lean#L149-L154","name":"Lean.Meta.Simp.Step.done","line":149,"kind":"ctor","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Step.done","doc":"For `pre` procedures, it returns the result without visiting any subexpressions.\n\nFor `post` procedures, it returns the result.\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">constructor</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Step.done\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Simp</span>.<span class=\"name\">Step</span>.<span class=\"name\">done</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(r : <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Result\">Lean.Meta.Simp.Result</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Step\">Lean.Meta.Simp.Step</a></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/