r the term being simplified.\nIf a simplification procedure result depends on this value,\nthen it is its reponsability to set `Result.cache := false`.\n\nMotivation for this field:\nSuppose we have a simplication procedure for normalizing arithmetic terms.\nThen, given a term such as `t_1 + ... + t_n`, we don't want to apply the procedure\nto every subterm `t_1 + ... + t_i` for `i < n` for performance issues. The procedure\ncan accomplish this by checking whether the parent term is also an arithmetical expression\nand do nothing if it is. However, it should set `Result.cache := false` to ensure\nwe don't miss simplification opportunities. For example, consider the following:\n```\nexample (x y : Nat) (h : y = 0) : id ((x + x) + y) = id (x + x) := by\n  simp_arith only\n  ...\n```\nIf we don't set `Result.cache := false` for the first `x + x`, then we get\nthe resulting state:\n```\n... |- id (2*x + y) = id (x + x)\n```\ninstead of\n```\n... |- id (2*x + y) = id (2*x)\n```\nas expected.\n\nRemark: given an application `f a b c` the \"parent\" term for `f`, `a`, `b`, and `c`\nis `f a b c`.\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Context.parent?\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Simp</span>.<span class=\"name\">Context</span>.<span class=\"name\">parent?</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(self : <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Context\">Lean.Meta.Simp.Context</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Lean.Expr</a></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/df668f00e6c08cb63661aacc43d0e83388e2c60d/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.lean#L59-L59","name":"Lean.Meta.Simp.Context.congrTheorems","line":59,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Context.congrTheorems","doc":""},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Context.congrTheorems\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Simp</span>.<span class=\"name\">Context</span>.<span class=\"name\">congrTheorems</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(self : <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Context\">Lean.Meta.Simp.Context</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/SimpCongrTheorems.html#Lean.Meta.SimpCongrTheorems\">Lean.Meta.SimpCongrTheorems</a></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/df668f00e6c08cb63661aacc43d0e83388e2c60d/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.lean#L58-L58","name":"Lean.Meta.Simp.Context.simpTheorems","line":58,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Context.simpTheorems","doc":""},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Context.simpTheorems\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Simp</span>.<span class=\"name\">Context</span>.<span class=\"name\">simpTheorems</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(self : <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Context\">Lean.Meta.Simp.Context</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/SimpTheorems.html#Lean.Meta.SimpTheoremsArray\">Lean.Meta.SimpTheoremsArray</a></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/df668f00e6c08cb63661aacc43d0e83388e2c60d/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.lean#L57-L57","name":"Lean.Meta.Simp.Context.maxDischargeDepth","line":57,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Context.maxDischargeDepth","doc":"`maxDischargeDepth` from `config` as an `UInt32`. "},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Context.maxDischargeDepth\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Simp</span>.<span class=\"name\">Context</span>.<span class=\"name\">maxDischargeDepth</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(self : <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Context\">Lean.Meta.Simp.Context</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#UInt32\">UInt32</a></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/df668f00e6c08cb63661aacc43d0e83388e2c60d/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.lean#L55-L55","name":"Lean.Meta.Simp.Context.config","line":55,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Context.config","doc":""},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Context.config\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Simp</span>.<span class=\"name\">Context</span>.<span class=\"name\">config</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(self : <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Context\">Lean.Meta.Simp.Context</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./In